```ts
Add two 3D points together.
const result = math.addVectors(
    { x: 1, y: 2, z: 3 },
    { x: 5, y: 6, z: 7 }
);

os.toast(result); // { x: 6, y: 8, z: 10 }
```

```ts
Add arbitrary numbers together.
const result = math.addVectors(
    { salary: 1000, tax: 50 },
    { salary: 5000, tax: 250 },
    { salary: 750, tax: 37.5 },
);

os.toast(result); // { salary: 6750, tax: 337.5 }
```

